Original workout description: Looking for a challenging full-body HIIT workout you can do anywhere? This 30-minute bodyweight routine has no repeats and no rest! You'll power through every move with intensity and precision. Best part? No equipment needed! Get ready to burn fat, build strength, and push your limits. Perfect for those who want a fast-paced, effective workout to fit into a busy schedule.
